One person's just
as good as another.

712
01:50:40,648 --> 01:50:45,984
Is it because you' re going away
to have your child?

713
01:50:46,120 --> 01:50:48,315
I had mine in a turnip patch.

714
01:50:48,455 --> 01:50:51,151
But it was the same old
whoremonger, wasn't it?

715
01:50:52,893 --> 01:50:54,690
Signe... Signe.

716
01:50:57,031 --> 01:51:00,728
Go up to the old whoremonger.
I'm afraid of the Missus.

717
01:51:02,736 --> 01:51:04,533
- Come on.
- Let me go!

718
01:51:06,040 --> 01:51:09,669
Kongstrup, come out and
heIp an old sweetheart!

719
01:51:09,810 --> 01:51:12,278
Let me go! Let me go!

720
01:51:13,214 --> 01:51:15,182
Get out! Out!

721
01:52:22,416 --> 01:52:23,815
What are you staring at?

722
01:52:39,633 --> 01:52:41,828
- Why are you late?
- Sorry.

723
01:53:00,621 --> 01:53:02,316
I don't understand.

724
01:53:02,790 --> 01:53:06,487
Only death can put an end
to grief so quickly.

725
01:53:07,127 --> 01:53:09,823
She must have a damned
good grip on herseIf.

726
01:54:25,439 --> 01:54:27,771
Wake u p and fetch the doctor.
Quick!

727
01:54:31,245 --> 01:54:35,739
- What is it, papa?
- I don't know.

728
01:54:43,123 --> 01:54:45,853
What is it? What happened?

729
01:54:46,493 --> 01:54:49,894
- It's so terrible.
- She cut him.

730
01:54:50,030 --> 01:54:52,624
- The Missus cut him.
- What happened?

731
01:54:54,535 --> 01:54:59,029
The Missus cut him.
